 13→# WP02: Event Bus
 14→
 15→**Implementation command**: `spec-kitty implement WP02 --base WP01`
 16→**Target repo**: `joyus-ai`
 17→**Dependencies**: WP01 (Schema & Foundation)
 18→**Priority**: P1 | Can run in parallel with WP03
